---
title: Hot 'N' Hearty Chicken Pizzas with Zucchini, Italian Herbs, and Chili Flakes
description: Chicken, cheese, and a crispy crust: they’re three Cs that are guaranteed to make your mouth do the cha-cha. If that’s not enough reason to check out this pizza recipe, how about juicy roasted zucchini, Italian herbs, and a layer of tomato sauce? Still haven’t hit “select”? Well then, champ, maybe the chili flakes on top will be enough to make you chuffed for that spicy finishing touch.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/hot-n-hearty-chicken-pizzas-28f1e7a1.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/hot-n-hearty-chicken-pizzas-5a99c7c9ae08b575c96a3012-dfdd55e5.pdf
